docs.lead_paragraph: Jerome Roth, oboist of the New York Philharmonic, is a bicyclist. William Blossom, a NYP bass player, is a juggler; and Myor Rosen, the harpist, is a chess fanatic. Nancy Donaruma, one of the NYP cellists, cooks Italian food. Paige Brook, the flutist, sails radio-controlled model ships. Jim Candido, one of the bass players, is a skier.
